---
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-20 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto border-t border-zinc-900/50">
  <!-- Glow Accent -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/3 left-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-teal-500/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 space-y-12">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <div class="text-xs font-mono text-zinc-555 uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2">
        <span>02 //</span>
        <span>My Background</span>
        <span class="h-[1px] w-12 bg-zinc-800"></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-sans font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
        About Me
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Split -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 md:gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Biography Text (Col Span 7) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-6 text-zinc-400 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed font-sans">
        <p>
          Hello! My name is Mahdi Imantaka Sutejo. I am a software engineer focused on building robust, high-performance web applications and data systems. I enjoy creating solutions that sit at the intersection of clean backend design and fluid, intuitive user interfaces.
        </p>
        <p>
          My interest in software engineering stems from a desire to solve real-world problems with high-efficiency code. Whether designing real-time network monitors, building distributed API gateways, or setting up secure data pipelines, I strive for clean architecture and detail-oriented implementation.
        </p>
        <p>
          Here are some of the key technologies and tools I've been working with recently:
        </p>

        <!-- Tech Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-2 gap-x-4 pt-2 font-mono text-xs text-zinc-350">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-teal-500">▹</span> TypeScript / JavaScript
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-teal-500">▹</span> Go
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-teal-500">▹</span> Rust
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-teal-500">▹</span> Astro / React
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-teal-500">▹</span> Tailwind CSS
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-teal-500">▹</span> Apache Kafka / Redis
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-teal-500">▹</span> Google BigQuery
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-teal-500">▹</span> Docker / Kubernetes
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo Column (Col Span 5) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex justify-center md:justify-end">
        <!-- Interactive Tech Frame Wrapper -->
        <div class="relative group w-64 aspect-square xs:w-72 sm:w-80 md:w-full max-w-[320px]">
          <!-- Background decorative tech lines -->
          <div class="absolute -inset-3 border border-zinc-900/60 rounded-lg pointer-events-none transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-102"></div>
          
          <!-- Glowing backdrop -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-teal-500/10 rounded-lg blur-md opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
          
          <!-- Outer border shifting offset -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 border border-teal-500/30 rounded-lg translate-x-2.5 translate-y-2.5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1.5 group-hover:translate-y-1.5 pointer-events-none"></div>

          <!-- Main Image Frame -->
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 w-full h-full">
            <img 
              src="/images/profile.jpg" 
              alt="Mahdi Imantaka Sutejo" 
              width="400"
              height="400"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale contrast-110 brightness-95 group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500"
            />
            
            <!-- Tech corner markers/viewfinders -->
            <div class="absolute top-2 left-2 w-3 h-3 border-t border-l border-teal-500/40 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-2 right-2 w-3 h-3 border-t border-r border-teal-500/40 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-2 left-2 w-3 h-3 border-b border-l border-teal-500/40 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 w-3 h-3 border-b border-r border-teal-500/40 pointer-events-none"></div>

            <!-- Overlay subtle color wash -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-teal-500/5 mix-blend-multiply group-hover:opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Label indicating photo can be replaced -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 left-0 right-0 text-center text-[10px] font-mono text-zinc-650 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">
            [SRC: /images/profile.jpg]
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
